social_posts.post_text: As the year 2023 approaches I am currently in the process of rebranding myself ! While I’m doing that I wanted to share two of my creations that just touch my heart ♥️ hopefully you let me know if they did the same for you in the “comments” #ThisIsAnopenspace

I love the scenery, I love the song, I love the energy, even though I look rough I love the emotion it gives ! Y’all been asking so it’s Dropping Tonight !! My brothers @jaleelanthonytv and @antshotthat773  killed this visual 🙏🏾

Today was such an amazing day ! Thank you @michaelairhartexperience for helping me surprise my High school principal @byronstingily today and allowing me to have such an emotional moment 🙏🏾 we danced, I tried to hug every singe kid in the building, I prayed over the school ! The mayor of Dolton pulled up and spoke to the kids and it was so fulfilling ! God Is Amazing to me 🙏🏾 my old principle was a key factor in my life when I was young and without his guidance I would have been lost ! So thank you again for being for loving the youth and being passionate about seeing change @byronstingily 🙏🏾

Grand rising my Kings and Queens ! I’m excited to announce that I’m dropping My new Single Called “ Let Go & Let God “ at the top of the year !! Moment of transparency ! 

I’m such a lover boy, I love being in love. I really love giving it, it makes me feel whole 😊 I’m a every affectionate person and my love language is touch. My downfall is that I’m every emotional, but I genuinely care so shit be a little more intense for me ! I’m a protector, I’m a provider ! I’ll give you my first and my last. I told myself by 25 I wanted to be someone’s husband, I wanted a family but I’m 27 and single. I’ve lost some of the most important people in my life ( my mother, grandmother, grandfather, Bestfriend, my brother) I have a slight abandonment issue, I hate being alone but I’m working on it, I’m territorial but I’m over confident ! My biggest down fall is I look for the love of my mother through a woman that barely knows me and it never works for me ! In conclusion I’m god fearing ! He is number 1 in my life and he lives through me….. my apologies I just need y’all to understand this new album 🗣️
My bunny hop still unbeaten 😂‼️🐐 what was your favorite move ??

A moment of transparency! I was a little skeptical about putting this album out. Not because I doubted the body of work, but because I’m just so unfamiliar with my support system at this moment in my career. But I’m finally breaking out of that shell and allowing you guys into my world, showing my personality, showing my character showing who I am when I’m in love, showing who I am when I’m against something.  etc ! I am being my most vulnerable self with this body of work. Also, putting on for the west side of Chicago 💯 I am a true 290 baby. My birthday is coming up and I’m having a birthday/release party on August 15 and it would mean the world to me if you’re in Chicago that you pull up and come experience real music. Party details coming tomorrow but my West side story will be available on all streaming platforms August 15. ♌️🙏🏾‼️

Appreciation post ! 

A few years ago I lost my biological mother 🕊️ and that is by far the hardest thing I ever had to deal with !! But my god always is present, he blessed me with this wonderful woman to call MOM 🙏🏾♥️ been in my life since I was like 8-9 year old. Never once made me feel different from her other kids, whatever I needed she made sure I had. From martial things, to Tough love, to advice about love, to financial direction. when I didn’t have a place to stay, one call and I’m walking through her front door with all my things and she there with open arms. I’m so blessed that I get the satisfaction of seeing you grow, seeing you be a perfect example for us ( your kids ) ! Seeing you go through the tuff moments with your chin up and so fearless. I thank god every day for blessing me with an angel like you mama ! Love you with every thing in me ♥️♥️ GG’s @lynayalove

Blessings my social media family ! 

So y’all know my mother passed away a few years ago 💔 we’ll long story short, this guy reached out to me and saying basically he my father. I was in my early mid 20’s at the time maybe 24-25 years old. I went through all his social media and this man was damn near twin. I couldn’t believe how we resembled each other.
